# $Header: /var/cvsroot/gentoo-x86/media-sound/alsa-utils/ChangeLog,v 1.390 2015/07/16 17:56:18 ago Exp $

  16 Jul 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #550214

  16 Jul 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #550214

  04 Jul 2015; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha, bug 550214

  29 May 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  arm stable wrt bug #550214

  28 May 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Stable for PPC64 (bug #550214).

  28 May 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #550214).

  27 May 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #550214

  23 May 2015; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  amd64 stable wrt bug #550214

*alsa-utils-1.0.29 (25 Mar 2015)

  25 Mar 2015; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +alsa-utils-1.0.29.ebuild:
  Version bump, as requested by Manuel Rüger in bug #541798.

  23 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #522038

  23 Nov 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #522038

  21 Nov 2014; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha, bug 522038

*alsa-utils-1.0.28-r1 (19 Nov 2014)

  19 Nov 2014; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +alsa-utils-1.0.28-r1.ebuild,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.28-aplay-return.patch,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.28-mixer-proto.patch,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.28-monitor-proto.patch,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.28-va-end.patch:
  Add various fixes from upstream.

  08 Nov 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  ppc/ppc64 stable wrt #522038

  02 Nov 2014; Sven Vermeulen <swift@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.27.2.ebuild,
  alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  Remove sec-policy/selinux-* dependency from DEPEND but keep in RDEPEND (bug
  #527698)

  23 Oct 2014; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  amd64/x86 stable, bug #522038

  21 Sep 2014; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #522038

  04 Sep 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #522038).

*alsa-utils-1.0.28 (23 Jun 2014)

  23 Jun 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> +alsa-utils-1.0.28.ebuild,
  +files/alsasound.initd-r6:
  Version bump wrt #513670 by "PG". Don't save pulseaudio state files to
  filesystem root directory / wrt #438844 by Alexander Tsoy.

  05 Apr 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove unused USE="minimal" description from metadata.xml

  05 Apr 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  -alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.27.1-r1.ebuild,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.23-modprobe.d.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.25-separate-usr-var-fs.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.26-kmod.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.27.1-hctl_elem_search.patch:
  old

