*alsa-utils-1.0.27.2 (18 Jul 2013)

  18 Jul 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.27.2.ebuild:
  Version bump wrt #477282 by Naohiro Aota and Rafał Mużyło

  15 Jul 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  -alsa-utils-1.0.27-r1.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.27.1.ebuild,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.27-alsactl.patch,
