*alsa-utils-1.0.27.1-r1 (27 May 2013)

  27 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.27.1-r1.ebuild,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.27.1-hctl_elem_search.patch:
  Include upstreamized patch for "hctl element search" wrt #468690 by William
  Throwe and Jaroslav Kysela

*alsa-utils-1.0.27.1 (27 May 2013)

  27 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.27.1.ebuild:
  Version bump; /lib/udev/rules.d/90-alsa-restore.rules has been removed in
  favour of the alsasound init script for reliable behavior with separate /var
  partition.

  02 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  alsa-utils-1.0.27-r1.ebuild:
  keepdir /usr/share/alsa/ucm to silence this warning (or error):
  ALSA lib parser.c:1266:(uc_mgr_scan_master_configs)

  01 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  alsa-utils-1.0.27-r1.ebuild:
  Call epatch_user wrt #468162 by Doug Goldstein

  01 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  -alsa-utils-1.0.27.ebuild:
  old

*alsa-utils-1.0.27-r1 (01 May 2013)

  01 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.27-r1.ebuild, +files/alsa-utils-1.0.27-alsactl.patch,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.27-arecord.patch,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.27-service.patch:
  Fix typing error in alsa-restore.service systemd file. Fix missing break to
  the capture loop in arecord. Fix buffer overflow in alsactl wrt #468160 by
  "John"

  01 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  -alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild,
  -alsa-utils-1.0.26.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.26-r1.ebuild,
  -alsa-utils-1.0.26-r3.ebuild, -files/alsasound.confd-r3,
  -files/alsasound.initd-r4:
  old

*alsa-utils-1.0.27 (01 May 2013)

  01 May 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.27.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*alsa-utils-1.0.26-r3 (19 Apr 2013)

  19 Apr 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.26-r3.ebuild:
  Remove alsaconf utility; doesn't work with depmod from sys-apps/kmod because
  it doesn't generate "modules.pcimap" and "modules.usbmap" files anymore like
  sys-apps/module-init-tools used to wrt #456214

  12 Apr 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #463451

  12 Apr 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #463451).

  05 Apr 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #463451

  05 Apr 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #463451

  02 Apr 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for arm, wrt bug #463451

  02 Apr 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for sh, wrt bug #463451

  01 Apr 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #463451

  31 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #463451

  30 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #463451

  30 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #463451

  27 Mar 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild:
  Remove redudant toolchain-funcs from inherit and show postinst msgs only for
  first install wrt #440448 by "poletti.marco"

  13 Mar 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #406101

*alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2 (08 Feb 2013)

  08 Feb 2013; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.26-r2.ebuild, +files/alsa-utils-1.0.26-kmod.patch:
  Patch out the call to update-modules script that was installed with
  sys-apps/module-init-tools and is not present with sys-apps/kmod.

  11 Dec 2012; Ian Stakenvicius <axs@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.26.ebuild,
  alsa-utils-1.0.26-r1.ebuild:
  virtualize udev by using udev.eclass to determine udevdir

*alsa-utils-1.0.26-r1 (06 Nov 2012)

  06 Nov 2012; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> +alsa-utils-1.0.26-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Add USE="ncurses libsamplerate" to control utils that use the respective libs,
  and expand USE=minimal to control alsa-info (which uses dialog) #441982.

  09 Sep 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  -alsa-utils-1.0.23-r1.ebuild, -files/alsa-utils-1.0.23-alsactl-output.patch,
  -files/alsa-utils-1.0.23-alsactl-output2.patch, -alsa-utils-1.0.25.ebuild,
  -alsa-utils-1.0.25-r2.ebuild, -alsa-utils-1.0.25-r3.ebuild:
  old

*alsa-utils-1.0.26 (09 Sep 2012)

  09 Sep 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.26.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*alsa-utils-1.0.25-r3 (10 Aug 2012)

  10 Aug 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.25-r3.ebuild:
  Query correct udevdir from udev.pc pkg-config file.

  23 Jul 2012; <swift@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.23-r1.ebuild,
  alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild, alsa-utils-1.0.25.ebuild,
  alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild, alsa-utils-1.0.25-r2.ebuild:
  Adding optional dependency on SELinux policy module

*alsa-utils-1.0.25-r2 (08 Apr 2012)

  08 Apr 2012; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +alsa-utils-1.0.25-r2.ebuild:
  Make sure that the minimal USE flag also does not install the alsaconf script,
  not just ignore the dependency.

  01 Apr 2012; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sh/sparc stable wrt #406101

  15 Mar 2012; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #406101

  15 Mar 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  marked x86 per bug 406101

  06 Mar 2012; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  Marking alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1 ppc64 stable for bug 406101

  29 Feb 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #406101

  29 Feb 2012; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #406101).

*alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1 (20 Feb 2012)

  20 Feb 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +alsa-utils-1.0.25-r1.ebuild,
  +files/alsasound.confd-r4, +files/alsasound.initd-r5:
  Use -I option on alsactl restore to avoid aborting unnecessarily, as per Adam
  Nielsen in bug #281631. libsamplerate is both a build & run time dependency,
  as per Albert W. Hopkins in bug #403557. Remove unsupported autoload/unload
  as it breaks with kmod, as per Ulenrich in bug #404535.

  18 Jan 2012; William Hubbs <williamh@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.23-r1.ebuild,
  alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  drop module-init-tools from dependencies since it is in @system and will
  eventually be replaced by kmod (approved by chainsaw).

  29 Dec 2011; Mark Loeser <halcy0n@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc/ppc64; bug #379423

  23 Oct 2011; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> files/alsasound.initd-r4:
  non-maintainer commit: Replaced deprecated opts variable in init script (bug
  #381893).

  23 Oct 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sh/sparc stable wrt #379423

  04 Oct 2011; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #379423

  20 Sep 2011; Andreas Schuerch <nativemad@gentoo.org>
  alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  x86 stable per bug 379423, thanks JD and Myckel

  25 Aug 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #379423).

  17 Aug 2011; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> alsa-utils-1.0.24.2-r1.ebuild:
  Mark stable on AMD64 based on my own testing; related to the packages in bug
  #379423 filed by Arun Raghavan.

