*alsa-utils-1.0.23 (16 Apr 2010)

  16 Apr 2010; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +alsa-utils-1.0.23.ebuild,
  +files/alsa-utils-1.0.23-modprobe.d.patch:
  Version bump. Input validation has been added to alsamixer. alsactl now
  features improved debugging features.

